name: GU Roctane Blueberry Pomegranate Gel
description: This gel shot contains an amino acid blend designed to provide nutritional support for extended sessions and endurance sports. The Roctane blend is fuel for activities that require focus, concentration and sustained mental acuity.Contains 35g of caffeine.Ingredients: maltodextrin, water fructose, leucine, sodium citrate, valine, natural flavours, malic acid, potassium citrate, citric acid, calcium carbonate, sea salt, green tea (leaf) extract (contains caffeine), isoleucine, gellan gum, sodium benzoate, potassium sorbate, D-alpha-tocopheryl acetate (natural Vitamin E).
